cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to an invalid value of 999 will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper PRACH setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為無效值 999 會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的 PRACH 設置。
